1. *Rastu* stabla u mom dvorištu. (The trees *are growing* in my yard.)
2. Kada *rastu* deca, postaju veoma radoznala. (When children *grow*, they become very curious.)
3. Moje finansije *rastu* svakog meseca. (My finances *are growing* every month.)
4. Ovde *raste* mnogo lekovitog bilja. (A lot of medicinal plants *grow* here.)
5. *Rastući* troškovi održavanja kuće me zabrinjavaju. (The *growing* costs of maintaining the house worry me.)
6. Da bi uspeo, moraš *rasti* kao osoba. (To succeed, you must *grow* as a person.)
7. Zemlja je *rastuća* ekonomija u ovom regionu. (The country is a *growing* economy in this region.)
8. Sazreo je i *rastao* kao umetnik tokom godina. (He matured and *grew* as an artist over the years.)
9. Povrće *raste* u bašti brže u proleće. (Vegetables *grow* faster in the garden in the spring.)
10. Tvoja ljubav prema knjigama je lepa stvar koja će *rasti* tokom vremena. (Your love for books is a beautiful thing that will *grow* over time.)